title: Step2 Love & Care Deluxe Nursery
description: The Love & Care Deluxe Nursery by Step2 is an all-in-one nursery that has everything toddlers will need to take care of their baby dolls. Little ones will learn about nurturing playing as they pretend to be just like mommy and daddy! This toy nursery will be the perfect addition to any child’s playroom or bedroom.

asset.description:
The Love & Care Deluxe Nursery by Step2 is an all-in-one nursery that has everything toddlers will need to take care of their baby dolls. Little ones will learn about nurturing playing as they pretend to be just like mommy and daddy! This toy nursery will be the perfect addition to any child’s playroom or bedroom. 

Learn more at: http://www.step2.com/p/Love-Care-Deluxe-Nursery

transcripts: Little ones will love playing mommy with this play nursery center. Large enough for several kids to play together, this nursery features all the essentials to take care of baby from changing table and washer to a high chair and sink. Done feeding baby, it's time to do the dishes the faucet even swiffles, even baby dolls need a nap help little baby to sleep by spinning the mobil. Make sure baby clothes get nice and clean, the clear washer door lets baby see inside and they can turn the clicker knob for added pretend play. Once the laundry is done hang baby's clothes on included hangers to keep from wrinkling. Storage won't be an issue with this play nursery set once play time fun is done all baby essentials can be neatly tucked away in the storage cabinet on top and bottom storage shelves or in the included storage bins. Made in the USA with some imported parts, the love and care deluxe nursery center made of strong durable materials that will last for years of play. The love and care deluxe nursery by step2.
